{
  "app": {
    "name": "Research Planning Agent Test Workflow",
    "mode": "workflow",
    "description": "Initial Dify workflow DSL for module-5 research planning agent. Import into the empty workflow at http://115.190.208.240:31880/workflow/289a1LGKdhR84gEN and choose a model before publishing.",
    "icon": "🧪",
    "icon_background": "#E0F2FE"
  },
  "workflow": {
    "features": {
      "file_upload": {
        "enabled": false
      }
    },
    "graph": {
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "start",
          "type": "custom",
          "data": {
            "type": "start",
            "title": "Start",
            "variables": [
              {
                "variable": "task_id",
                "label": "task_id",
                "type": "text-input",
                "required": true,
                "max_length": 128
              },
              {
                "variable": "iteration",
                "label": "iteration",
                "type": "number",
                "required": true
              },
              {
                "variable": "question_card",
                "label": "question_card",
                "type": "paragraph",
                "required": true
              },
              {
                "variable": "hypothesis_evidence_packages",
                "label": "hypothesis_evidence_packages",
                "type": "paragraph",
                "required": true
              },
              {
                "variable": "planning_constraints",
                "label": "planning_constraints",
                "type": "paragraph",
                "required": false
              },
              {
                "variable": "user_constraints",
                "label": "user_constraints",
                "type": "paragraph",
                "required": false
              }
            ]
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 80,
            "y": 240
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "llm_research_plan",
          "type": "custom",
          "data": {
            "type": "llm",
            "title": "Generate Research Plan JSON",
            "model": {
              "provider": "",
              "name": "",
              "mode": "chat",
              "completion_params": {
                "temperature": 0.2,
                "max_tokens": 4096
              }
            },
            "prompt_template": [
              {
                "role": "system",
                "text": "你是研究计划输出 Agent。你必须只输出严格 JSON，不要 Markdown，不要代码块，不要解释文字。输出 schema_version 必须为 experiment_planner_output_v1。不得虚构不存在的参考文献、数据集 URL、真实实验结果或已经完成的实验。plan.references 只能来自输入 hypothesis_evidence_packages[].source_literature。rationale.logic_chain[].evidence_ids 只能来自输入证据包中的 evidence_subset。若 needs_more_evidence 为 true，必须生成 feedback_tasks，把缺失证据转为下一轮任务。"
              },
              {
                "role": "user",
                "text": "请根据以下输入生成研究计划 JSON。\n\n任务 ID：{{#start.task_id#}}\n迭代轮次：{{#start.iteration#}}\n\nquestion_card:\n{{#start.question_card#}}\n\nhypothesis_evidence_packages:\n{{#start.hypothesis_evidence_packages#}}\n\nplanning_constraints:\n{{#start.planning_constraints#}}\n\nuser_constraints:\n{{#start.user_constraints#}}\n\n必须输出如下顶层结构：\n{\n  \"schema_version\": \"experiment_planner_output_v1\",\n  \"agent_name\": \"ExperimentPlannerAgent\",\n  \"task_id\": \"{{#start.task_id#}}\",\n  \"iteration\": {{#start.iteration#}},\n  \"status\": \"success | partial_success | failed\",\n  \"plans\": []\n}\n\n每个 plans[] 必须包含 hypothesis_id、status、error_message、plan。plan 必须包含 problem_statement、rationale、technical_details、datasets、paper_title、paper_abstract、methods、experiments、results、references、feedback_tasks、limitations。"
              }
            ],
            "context": {
              "enabled": false
            },
            "vision": {
              "enabled": false
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 420,
            "y": 240
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "end",
          "type": "custom",
          "data": {
            "type": "end",
            "title": "End",
            "outputs": [
              {
                "variable": "research_plan",
                "value_selector": [
                  "llm_research_plan",
                  "text"
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 780,
            "y": 240
          }
        }
      ],
      "edges": [
        {
          "id": "start-to-llm",
          "source": "start",
          "target": "llm_research_plan",
          "data": {
            "sourceType": "start",
            "targetType": "llm"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "llm-to-end",
          "source": "llm_research_plan",
          "target": "end",
          "data": {
            "sourceType": "llm",
            "targetType": "end"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
